OL,3,CShipyard worker strikes will risk
OL,4,Cfurther delays to Clyde warships `
OL,5,Cunion
OL,7,FStrikes by shipyard workers will risk
OL,8,Fmore delays to Clyde-built warships,
OL,9,Funions have warned.
OL,11,FGMB Scotland said support staff
OL,12,Fsupplying tools, materials and
OL,13,Fequipment for BAE Systems shipyards on
OL,14,Fthe upper Clyde will strike on Monday
OL,15,Fafter rejecting a three-year pay offer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
