OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780880588
OL,3,CShipyard worker strikes will risk
OL,4,Cfurther delays to Clyde warships `
OL,5,Cunion
OL,7,FThe union said that planned strikes by
OL,8,Fshipyard workers employed by GXO
OL,9,FLogistics will risk disrupting the
OL,10,Falready-delayed construction of HMS
OL,11,FGlasgow, the first of eight Type 26
OL,12,Fanti-submarine frigates for the Royal
OL,13,FNavy.
OL,15,FThe workers claimed the offer does not
OL,16,Fmatch the deal secured by BAE staff or
OL,17,Fclose the salary gap between them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
