PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780880588
OL,3,CShipyard worker strikes will risk
OL,4,Cfurther delays to Clyde warships `
OL,5,Cunion
OL,7,FRory Steel, GMB Scotland organiser,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The work of these shipyards is
OL,9,Fbuilt on the experience, expertise and
OL,10,Fcommitment of our members.
OL,12,F"Logistics workers are fundamental to
OL,13,Fthe successful operation of these
OL,14,Fyards and GXO management must
OL,15,Funderstand their determination to
OL,16,Fensure their role is properly
OL,17,Frecognised and fairly rewarded."
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@AOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
