SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780880588
OL,3,CShipyard worker strikes will risk
OL,4,Cfurther delays to Clyde warships `
OL,5,Cunion
OL,7,FWorkers will strike at shipyards in
OL,8,FGovan and Scotstoun on Monday and
OL,9,FTuesday, at BAE Systems supply hubs at
OL,10,FLinwood, Renfrewshire, on Thursday and
OL,11,FEurocentral, Lanarkshire, on Friday.
OL,13,FGMB members rejected a three-year pay
OL,14,Fplan that would increase wages by 3.5%
OL,15,Fin the first year and 3% in each of
OL,16,Fthe following two years.
OL,18,FThe results of an official ballot
OL,19,Frevealed 97% of the workers backed
OL,20,Findustrial action with a turnout of
OL,21,F84%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780880588
OL,3,CShipyard worker strikes will risk
OL,4,Cfurther delays to Clyde warships `
OL,5,Cunion
OL,7,FMr Steel said the strikes were not
OL,8,F"only about pay" but "fairness and
OL,9,Frespect."
OL,11,FHe said: "Our members can't accept
OL,12,Fbeing underpaid for the work they do.
OL,13,FManagement must ensure the long-
OL,14,Fstanding pay gaps between GXO
OL,15,Fcolleagues and BAE workers is first
OL,16,Fcalculated and then closed.
OL,18,F"How can colleagues, working beside
OL,19,Feach other in similar roles of similar
OL,20,Fvalue, be paid differently?
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@PO]pD@VOUqD@IO]sD@JOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780880588
OL,3,CShipyard worker strikes will risk
OL,4,Cfurther delays to Clyde warships `
OL,5,Cunion
OL,7,F"BAE Systems brought GXO in to cut
OL,8,Fcosts but our members are not prepared
OL,9,Fto accept wages below their worth.
OL,11,F"This not only about pay but fairness
OL,12,Fand respect and needs to be addressed
OL,13,Fwith urgency."
OL,15,FA BAE Systems spokesperson said: "This
OL,16,Fis a matter for GXO Logistics and its
OL,17,Fworkforce.
OL,19,F"We have made temporary arrangements
OL,20,Fto minimise any impact to our
OL,21,Factivities from the strike action."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUuD@NO]wD@bOU{D@AOU}D@cO]
